<p>Long-range planning sets the foundation for a successful DFW event. During this phase, focus on the major decisions that shape everything else:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Set Your Budget</strong> -- Determine your total event budget and allocate funds across categories: venue, catering, entertainment (including photo booth), decor, and miscellaneous expenses. In the DFW market, a premium photo booth rental typically falls within your entertainment budget alongside DJ or live music costs.</li>
